The ''Slovenia national under-19 football team'' is the national under-19 football team of [[Slovenia]] and is controlled by the [[Football Association of Slovenia]].

==Current squad==
The following players were named in the squad for the [[2012 UEFA European Under-19 Football Championship qualification|European U19 Championship First Qualifying Round]], running between 21â26 September 2011. The games are against [[Belgium national under-19 football team|Belgium]], [[Scotland national under-19 football team|Scotland]] and [[Wales national under-19 football team|Wales]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nzs.si/reprezentance/U19=sl|title=U19 kvalifikacije za EP 2012|work=NZS|accessdate=}}</ref>

